IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. INSPECTSET.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-S PIC X(10) VALUE 'AAABBBCCC'.
01 WS-N PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.
01 WS-C PIC X(10) VALUE 'HELLO123'.
01 WS-I PIC 9(3) VALUE 5.
01 WS-J PIC 9(3) VALUE 10.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
    INSPECT WS-S TALLYING WS-N FOR LEADING 'A'.
    DISPLAY WS-N.
    INSPECT WS-C CONVERTING '0123456789' TO 'XXXXXXXXXX'.
    DISPLAY WS-C.
    SET WS-I TO 99.
    DISPLAY WS-I.
    SET WS-J UP BY 5.
    DISPLAY WS-J.
    SET WS-J DOWN BY 3.
    DISPLAY WS-J.
    STOP RUN.
